this_title: Last Week Tonight With John Oliver Season 12

introduction: HBO has renewed Last Week Tonight for a further three seasons, taking the weekly show through 2026.The new deal, which runs through Season 13, comes as the tenth season of the late-night show is coming to a close later this month.
